# Typography Rules (STRICT)

## DO NOT MODIFY
- font-display / font-sans / font-mono
- any className containing font-related utilities
- globals.css font variables (--font-body, --font-display, --font-mono)
- body typography (letter-spacing, line-height, font smoothing)
- layout.tsx font injection

## ALLOWED
- import v0 components as-is
- connect data props
- adjust import paths
- minimal wrapper for AppShell

## VIOLATION
Any modification to typography is strictly forbidden.
If modification seems necessary, STOP and report instead of changing.
